{%- style -%}
  .about-section {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: white;
  }

  .about-container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-image {
    position: relative;
    height: 24rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .about-image:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .about-image::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, white, transparent);
  }

  .about-content {
    order: 2;
  }

  .about-label {
    font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #2D8659;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2C2C2C;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .about-title-highlight {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .about-title-highlight::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -0.5rem;
    left: 0;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 0.125rem;
    background: #2D8659;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-text-secondary {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: #2D8659;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: gap 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: none;
    border: none;
  }

  .about-cta:hover {
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-section {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .about-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .about-content {
      order: 1;
    }

    .about-image {
      order: 2;
      height: 20rem;
    }

    .about-title {
      font-size: 1.875rem;
    }

    .about-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
{%- endstyle -%}

<section class="about-section" id="about">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-image">
      <img 
        src="https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663559062373/6PkbiX5sXEC8bHAdezvwj7/about-bg-K2mVy3CsXLtN7PCWvqWPVU.webp" 
        alt="ECOTech 비전"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <span class="about-label">ECOTech 소개</span>
      
      <h2 class="about-title">
        <span class="about-title-highlight">신뢰할 수 있는 파트너</span>
        <br>
        <span style="color: #4b5563; font-weight: 300;">고객과 함께 성장합니다</span>
      </h2>

      <p class="about-text">
        ECOTech는 국제 무역, 디지털 마케팅, IT 솔루션, 첨단 산업 장비, 부동산, 마케팅 컨설팅, 플랜트 사업 등 다양한 분야에서 고객과 함께 성장하는 기업입니다.
      </p>

      <p class="about-text-secondary">
        친환경 가치와 신뢰를 바탕으로, 투명하고 정직한 거래를 추구합니다. 각 분야의 전문성을 바탕으로 고객의 성공을 함께 만들어가고 있습니다.
      </p>

      <button class="about-cta" onclick="document.querySelector('#contact').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'})">
        더 알아보기
        <span>→</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
